%HRTitleEvent Jacoby
[Event "Baker Bridge - Jacoby 2NT / Splinters"]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "1"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "W:93.9753.K2.AJT42 AQJT8.QJ2.84.Q53 52.A84.QJT76.976 K764.KT6.A953.K8"]
[Declarer "N"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "W"]
pass 1S pass 2NT pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 1, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{You open 1\S and partner responds 2NT. What do you say next? 

With a minimum hand and no singletons you bid the game immediately. Partner has nothing to add so he passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "E:KQJ62.6.KJ75.A84 954.Q8432.AT62.9 AT87.KJ95.84.KQ3 3.AT7.Q93.JT7652"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
1S pass 2NT pass 3H pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 2, chOption: E, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 0, nRot: 1, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{With 14 points and good 4-card support you bid a Jacoby 2NT. Partner next bids 3\H.  

You couldn't hear much worse news. Partner has a singleton \H so your \H K J are not worth very much. You have nothing to do but return to the trump suit so you bid 4\S.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "S"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "S:AKT87.KQ5.JT84.8 432.T742.A93.Q95 QJ95.AJ63.K7.KT4 6.98.Q652.AJ7632"]
[Declarer "S"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "S"]
1S pass 2NT pass 3C pass 3H pass 3S pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: S, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 2, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{You have just a little extra so you bid 3\C to show a singleton. Partner says 3\H and it is your bid again. 

Partner's bid means he has first round \H control, obviously the \HA. But it also denies holding the \DA since control bids are made up-the-line. You show your lack of a Minor suit Ace by returning to 3\S. Partner signs off at game.

You could equally have just bid 4\S yourself.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "4"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "All"]
[Deal "W:AQJT8.K4.84.AQ83 752.T63.A3.T9754 K943.72.KQJ95.KJ 6.AQJ985.T762.62"]
[Declarer "W"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "W"]
1S pass 2NT pass 3NT pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 0, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{With opening hand and 4-card \S support this is an ideal Jacoby 2NT response. Partner says 3NT.  

West has some extra strength and a 5-card \S suit. This is the point in the bidding where you would make a control bid, showing an Ace. Well, you would if you actually had an Ace. The way you indicate your lack of a control is to just return the the agreed trump suit. So you bid 4\S and partner passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "5"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "N:AQJT85.K4.84.AT3 6.AQ932.JT9.9652 K973.J7.KQ65.KJ8 42.T865.A732.Q74"]
[Declarer "N"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
1S pass 2NT pass 3S pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 5, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{You show an above minimum hand with 6 trumps by bidding 3\S. Partner bids 4\S. What do you say next? 

Partner would have shown a red Ace if he had one. Since he doesn't have one, all thoughts of slam are off. You pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "6"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:A65.AT754.A7.862 J87.J.86542.KJ43 K3.KQ86.KQJ3.975 QT942.932.T9.AQT"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "4H"]
